    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5>Recipe 4: Caprese Salad</h5>
            <p>A classic Italian salad showcasing fresh tomatoes, creamy mozzarella, and fragrant basil, drizzled with balsamic glaze.</p>
            <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>3 large ripe tomatoes, sliced</li>
                <li>8 ounces fresh mozzarella cheese, sliced</li>
                <li>½ cup fresh basil leaves</li>
                <li>2 tablespoons balsamic glaze</li>
                <li>2 tablespoons extra virgin olive oil</li>
                <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
                <li>Optional garnish: freshly cracked black pepper, flaky sea salt</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
