            <h5>Recipe 5: Vegetable Stir-Fry</h5>
            <p>Quick and easy stir-fry loaded with colorful vegetables and tossed in a savory sauce, perfect for a healthy weeknight meal.</p>
            <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>2 tablespoons vegetable oil</li>
                <li>1 bell pepper, thinly sliced</li>
                <li>1 cup broccoli florets</li>
                <li>1 cup sliced carrots</li>
                <li>1 cup snow peas</li>
                <li>1 cup sliced mushrooms</li>
                <li>3 cloves garlic, minced</li>
                <li>1 tablespoon grated ginger</li>
                <li>¼ cup soy sauce</li>
                <li>2 tablespoons hoisin sauce</li>
                <li>1 tablespoon rice vinegar</li>
                <li>1 teaspoon sesame oil</li>
                <li>Optional garnish: chopped green onions, sesame seeds</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
